jobDetails.modificationDetails: 4 holes drilled in south wall kitchen.

scheduled.notes: Damage to boiler in main basement room of the building. Renter manually tried to adjust it and one of the pipes bursted.
Complaint from the renter about paint chipping off front-edge of the building. Send out inspector to report maintenance to be completed.
Annual inspection of Solar Panels on top of Hotel. No damage reported but full inspection required. Leave signed certificate at front-desk if completed, or quote for repairments if needed.
Renter modified main water tap in order to fit in a washing machine. Make an inspection of the adjusted water tap and confirm it's up to standards.
